{"tid":1674052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11月港殤紀念，全民戴花 – 以黃花紀念義士","createTime":"2019-10-25T03:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T15:29:43.000Z","uid":116278,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"406bdd7e4f68f1f6bc65c3f42e1b18b431b12bff","tid":1674052,"uid":116278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">11月港殤紀念，全民戴花 &ndash; 以黃花紀念義士</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國殤紀念日</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">(Remembrance Day)</span></span></strong> 訂立於每年的 11 月 11 日，為一個由英聯邦國家紀念在一戰、二戰和其他戰爭中犧牲的軍人與平民的紀念節日，又稱「和平紀念日」、「陣亡將士紀念日」。<br />\n<br />\n國殤紀念日一般會佩戴一種紅色的虞美人花（和罌粟花同屬不同種），佩戴的原因來自加拿大軍醫John McCrae的一首詩《在法蘭德斯戰場 (In Flanders Fields) 》，虞美人花被選擇是因為一戰最慘烈的戰場法蘭德斯盛開着虞美人花，而虞美人花的紅色代表壕溝中的鮮血。後來亦有人佩戴白色的罌粟花，他們認為這代表和平。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">虞美人花</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/fDmTOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2FfDmTOM.jpg&h=20fb428f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">In Flanders fields the poppies blow<br />\nBetween the crosses, row on row,<br />\n  That mark our place; and in the sky<br />\n  The larks, still bravely singing, fly<br />\nScarce heard amid the guns below.<br />\n<br />\nWe are the Dead. Short days ago<br />\nWe lived, felt dawn, saw sunset glow,<br />\n  Loved and were loved, and now we lie<br />\n      In Flanders fields.<br />\n<br />\nTake up our quarrel with the foe:<br />\nTo you from failing hands we throw<br />\n  The torch; be yours to hold it high.<br />\n  If ye break faith with us who die<br />\nWe shall not sleep, though poppies grow<br />\n      In Flanders fields.</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K6BlOkpdkg8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK6BlOkpdkg8&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=9ff4441a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K6BlOkpdkg8</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n我們團隊製作了一個黃色虞美人花襟針的設計圖，大家除了紀念當年英勇保衛香港的軍人，亦希望同時可以紀念近五個月以來，因反送中運動受傷、折騰，甚至結束自己生命的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n簡單版<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/3N9nue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2F3N9nue.jpg&h=f853a174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進階版<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/jFv3WU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2FjFv3WU.jpg&h=50d0f39a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十一月香港人要繼續遍地開花，讓極權政府知道我們並不會因惡法、施政報告無用的小恩小惠而退縮！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mgELDYH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmgELDYH.jpg&h=da5355cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c09Pmb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc09Pmb3.jpg&h=0e8b50c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十一月,齊上齊落齊FORWARD!<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/A9QSLf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2FA9QSLf.jpg&h=092e0f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n初階版LINK:<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/3N9nue.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2F3N9nue.jpg&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=b458ef84\" target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/3N9nue.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n進階版LINK:<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/jFv3WU.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2FjFv3WU.jpg&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=689b23d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/jFv3WU.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"49d1aa0e629bc1c1a2b50ae7edba5d3a58dc1c70","tid":1674052,"uid":153151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中</span><span style=\"color: green;\">華</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">民</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">族</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">必</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">須</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">瓦</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">解</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">，</span><span style=\"color: maroon;\">中</span><span style=\"color: teal;\">國</span><span style=\"color: navy;\">必</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">須</span><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>滅亡</ins></strong></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"540c0569866e6e80f22360185f696b93cf9a23b8","tid":1674052,"uid":116278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:50:34.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f2ec0135b3a20a8db59c5c16a336fcbf6e2f15","tid":1674052,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"1e84e3035c24dded9eb29d262cea1ebc5bd524a6","tid":1674052,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"支持，係戴起衫袋扣住? 原諒我咁問好膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab1ac5e86a768ba082118b26005e0065e87350f","tid":1674052,"uid":272951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"26361ad66504de0a53679c47f7391a64f19fb263","tid":1674052,"uid":116278,"li